FBIS3-37549 "drsov034_b_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-034 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Feb 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Signs Decree on Cadre Policy Council LD1702210594 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 2000 GMT 17 Feb 94 LD1702210594 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Russia's President Boris Yeltsin has signed a decree confirming the composition of the Council for Cadre Policy under the Russian head of state. It will consist of 17 people, including First Vice Premier Oleg Soskovets; Presidential Administration Chief Sergey Filatov; Federation Council Chairman Vladimir Shumeyko; Foreign Minister Andrey Kozyrev; and Moscow Mayor Yuriy Luzhkov. By another decree, the president appointed Boris Tyulkov his representative in Omsk Oblast.
